snippet.title: Alida game 15 Years Anniversary
snippet.description: Alida game was released 15 years ago in 2003. Alida was distributed by seven game publishers around the world for Macintosh and PC computers in seven languages. Alida was created and produced by independent Australian developer Cos Russo.
